{"title":"Salsa’s 2021 Warbird and Stormchaser Have New Colors and Build Specs","link":"https://theradavist.com/2021/03/salsas-2021-warbird-and-stormchaser-have-new-colors-and-build-specs/?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=salsas-2021-warbird-and-stormchaser-have-new-colors-and-build-specs","date":1615476664000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><section><article id=\"article-206898\"><div><p><img src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/20210126_SAL_Warbird_Studio_707647_003_cc.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" alt=\"Salsa’s 2021 Warbird and Stormchaser Have New Colors and Build Specs\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/20210126_SAL_Warbird_Studio_707647_003_cc.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w,https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/20210126_SAL_Warbird_Studio_707647_003_cc.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/20210126_SAL_Warbird_Studio_707647_003_cc.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" data-base-url=\"https://radavist-static-production.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/2021/03/20210126_SAL_Warbird_Studio_707647_003_cc.jpg\" data-base-quality=\"75\" data-alt-srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/20210126_SAL_Warbird_Studio_707647_003_cc.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w,https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/20210126_SAL_Warbird_Studio_707647_003_cc.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/20210126_SAL_Warbird_Studio_707647_003_cc.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\"></p></div><header><h4>Radar</h4></header><div><p><img src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/20210126_SAL_Warbird_Studio_707647_003_cc.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/20210126_SAL_Warbird_Studio_707647_003_cc.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/20210126_SAL_Warbird_Studio_707647_003_cc.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/20210126_SAL_Warbird_Studio_707647_003_cc.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" data-base-url=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/20210126_SAL_Warbird_Studio_707647_003_cc.jpg\" data-base-quality=\"75\" data-alt-srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/20210126_SAL_Warbird_Studio_707647_003_cc.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/20210126_SAL_Warbird_Studio_707647_003_cc.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/20210126_SAL_Warbird_Studio_707647_003_cc.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\"></p><p>Salsa’s flagship gravel bikes are back this year with new paint and new specs. The all-carbon Warbird still fits a 700c x 45 mm or 650b x 2.0″ with a racey geometry. New for 2021, the Warbird comes laced with AXS wide ($6,999) at the top end or Apex 1 ($2,799).</p><p><img src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/20210127_SAL_Stormchaser_Studio_707647_001_cc.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/20210127_SAL_Stormchaser_Studio_707647_001_cc.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/20210127_SAL_Stormchaser_Studio_707647_001_cc.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/20210127_SAL_Stormchaser_Studio_707647_001_cc.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" data-base-url=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/20210127_SAL_Stormchaser_Studio_707647_001_cc.jpg\" data-base-quality=\"75\" data-alt-srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/20210127_SAL_Stormchaser_Studio_707647_001_cc.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/20210127_SAL_Stormchaser_Studio_707647_001_cc.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/03/20210127_SAL_Stormchaser_Studio_707647_001_cc.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\"></p><p>The aluminum Stormchaser can cram a little bigger tires at 700c x 50 mm or 650b x 50 mm, yet is designed to be raced in muddy conditions with a 42mm tire for ample mud clearance. The Stormchaser also has a slacker head angle to battle the muck. The Stormchaser comes built as shown as a singlespeed ($1599) or as a frameset with a geared or singlespeed option ($1199).</p><p>See more at <a href=\"https://salsacycles.com/culture/fresh_gravel_new_warbird_stormchaser\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Salsa</a>.</p></div><nav><h4>Related</h4></nav></article></section></div>","author":"prolly","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"2dbeac19e823a66e1e5e0ea25b7f1096ada83b7273f59fd8443355c881f5f3e5","category":"Cycling"}